@Comment:	Time is 7:12
@Comment:	the letter is to the Terminator; After a lengthy discussion about how to spell Schwarzenegger (and I'm not sure if I have it right) , everyone agrees just to write to Terminator; This is a big spelling hurdle , and Mot won't let Chi use his Terminator Card and instead encourages him to break it down into component words such as term and in; The session is lively with good jokes about spelling Schwarzenegger , and Chi's writing skills seem to be okay; He puts dear in himself and spells it right , but puts a lowercase i for I until Mot corrects him; Chi and Mot discuss content of a letter before writing -- Chi describes writing a return address in school and Mot says there's more to letters than that; Chi determines text
@Comment:	Dear Terminator I want a reel Terminator
